metadata.name: CUBEHEART_LOVE2022N001
metadata.description: CubeHeart, which began in 2012, contains the autobiographical story of the artist's life. Jahyun Seo is a Visual artist who conducts visual perception experiments through the "Seeing and Being Showed" series, which contains images displayed in real space since 2016 in expanded virtual photos again. It contains the journey of life in the Cube Space, that is, the movement of cubes, and talks about life and death, good and evil, discernment of right and wrong, love and hope through color metaphors.
